            Insert.IntoTable(TableName.Job).WithIdentityInsert().Row(new { Id = 829, CreatedAt = DateTime.Parse("2018-05-18"), IsActive = true, Title = "Full Stack .NET/C# Developer", Description = "<p><b>GFR Media</b> offers the widest variety of media platforms in Puerto Rico, United States and Latin America. Our audience has made our brands the leading media platforms in the country and the main source of relevant information in Puerto Rico. Our brands, including the main newspapers in Puerto Rico, <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.elnuevodia.com/http://\">El Nuevo Día</a> and <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.primerahora.com/\">Primera Hora</a> are leaders in the segments of digital media, mobile and print newspapers in the country. <br><br>Our online products range everywhere from leading E-Commerce, Entertainment and Gastronomy content and Classifieds, brands like Oferta Del Día, Sal.pr, SHOP.pr, ClasificadosPR, Por Dentro, Magacín, Online Video Platforms, Mobile Apps and many more.<b><br></b></p><p><b>About the Team</b></p><p>We like to believe our team is top-notch, we joke a lot, eat a lot and program in a friendly environment yet we take our work very seriously and give it all to produce quality code. Everyone gets involved in steering what we do, providing ideas for development and opinions on technologies we use. The ideal candidate will bring that same spark to our team.</p><p><b>Requirements</b></p><p></p><ul><li>3+ years experience working with C#&nbsp;</li><li>Experience with ASP.NET MVC 4 or later</li><li>Experience with SQL Server</li><li>1+ year experience with AngularJS</li><li>Experience with integrating 3rd party APIs</li><li>Experience with Amazon Web Services is a plus</li><li>Experience with TDD &amp; BDD is a plus</li></ul>Consider these as bonus points, but not fully required for the position<br><ul><li>Experience with ReactJS and/or React Native</li><li>Have worked in any way upon an e-commerce